hi guys,

what is the best way to encrypt the bash_history file?
I try using crypt/decrypt with GPG when login/logout. It works, but not
safe enough.


Example:

On .bashrc: gpg -e -r "...UID..." .bash_history
 and on .bash_logout: gpg -d -e "...UID..." .bash_history





